OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMainly dry
OL,6,Fthis evening but rain spreading to the
OL,7,FWestern Isles. Then rain will spread
OL,8,Facross all parts overnight, becoming
OL,9,Fdrier along the west coast later.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FOvernight rain clearing
OL,12,Fduring the morning. Then bright spells
OL,13,Fand scattered showers, these turning
OL,14,Fheavy in the west later. Colder than
OL,15,Fof late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
