OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FDry and
OL,6,Fbright for most of Friday but
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain spreading northeast
OL,8,Fin the evening. Mainly dry Saturday, a
OL,9,Ffew showers in the west. Breezy with
OL,10,Fshowers on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
